Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THIS IS BEYOND CABLE THIS IS FIOS THIS IS BIG
Comment: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twitter on a laptop is too cool for me
Comment: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twitter on a 50" flat screen so you can search, send and receive tweets right from your couch without changing the channel...is really too cool for me.
Comment: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twitter, right on your TV, this is beyond cable, this is just stupid shit.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a cliff up ahead. If we keep going like this, it'll be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay inside the guard rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years after the date of my birth, I came face to face with true darkness for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear viewers, might you be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that large numbers of honeybees are said to be disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this nighttime orienteering deep in the mountains unfolding before you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is due to my own disappearance as a worker bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water over here tastes lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water over there tastes bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh heh, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk to the next train stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that'll be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly hell, and it's all that honey's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather, it's all because of my total infatuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H6C00C6&\fad(200,0)}J{\c&H000000&}-pwq
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was a freshman university student
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before me lay open countless doors to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\c&HAE7DE0&\3c&HF2F1FA&\bord3\be3\fad(200,300)}"Softball Circle {\c&H68C3F3&}Honwaka{\c&HAE7DE0&}"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H6636B1&\bord1\3c&HE8E4F7&\be2}"Recruiting"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Honwaka reserves a corner of the sports field each week and plays softball,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the occasional game thrown in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that it's totally free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The logo might say "softball circle,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like their main purpose is to engage in warm-hearted intermingling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here there is no practicing day and night chasing around white balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no sweat, no tears, no guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is aiming for any national tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, my melancholic high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would not be so bad to join with this bunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and while breaking into an invigorating sweat, make a hundred friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely master cordial conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while playing catch with beautiful women during early morning practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an ability that I must master to make my mark on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is most definitely not simply because I wish to converse with pretty girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn the art!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if, after mastering the art,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a beautiful woman wished to come with me, I would have no reason to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear not, and come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(652,180)\bord0\fad(200,300)\c&H333534&\fs38}"Softball Circle {\c&H229EE5&}Honwaka{\c&H333534&}"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately I was an idiot beyond all redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please listen carefully to the circumstances which befell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will accept no leaving in the middle of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The softball circle Honwaka was just as the name says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the covering clouds of a springtime haze, warm and snuggly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that interested me the most was their male/female ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an organic sandwich and tea with royal jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most definitely not that I judge everything primarily by such a criterion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but was not this the best possible ratio to nurture intimacy with the opposite sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that worried me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was that it was a bit too "warm and snuggly."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, everyone was far too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place doesn't use much pesticide, but the prices are quite reasonable, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of getting ducks to eat harmful insects is quite effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The consumer shouldn't have to suffer just because something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is more convenient for the producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People should at least have options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They take away the people's choice because they don't want them to get money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes you feel like a cup ramen, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the ones that are bad for you with lots of oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think adults have to set a proper example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can show the right attitude to the children, then our children will grow up normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that children who are loved properly from a young age don't go astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could cross the street on a red light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to teach them the concept of not blindly accepting the law without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long I was no longer part of the conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and every time I uttered a word
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone would fall silent with kind smiles still plastered on their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among those constantly brightly smiling faces, with no dissent or dirty talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a single man I felt close to named Ozu with a face like a youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his peculiar conversational skills he managed to secure his place within the circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he seemed to have trouble smiling and laughing innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving the impression of an evil that could not be hidden lurking inside his gut,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he had a laugh so unnatural it was like he wasn't born with the proper muscles to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say a drowning man will even gasp at straw,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I immediately hit it off with such a slippery fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone's fault for creating such a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could learn the art of pleasant sociability through such lukewarm interaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My patience had almost worn through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a situation that could explode at any time, like the Cuban Missile Crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, while I remained on the brink one day in the summer of my freshman year,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a fateful encounter which melted my heart in a warm embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her beauty was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like her "whoa" factor was of 100% purity,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like if you tried to speak with her she'd be too bright to look at directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed she was an important member of Honwaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she was surrounded by people,\N smiling as she listened to their conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed the state exam thanks to the royal jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grades rose thanks to those concentration patches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Honwaka that I've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the personification of the raven-haired maiden I pictured in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I walked with her along the mall of Sanjoukawara or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet people would surely be jealous looking at the fresh young couple walking down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at you. Should you be eating something so unhealthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neko Ramen is a mysterious food cart that only appears around Tadasu Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rumored they use actual cats to make the broth, but there's no proof of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner says it started living nearby after he began feeding it used bonito flakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if he was ever reported to the police I'm sure his cart would be shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the taste is unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohinata-san is a freshman like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me,\N I can tell what you're thinking at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's the only daughter of the health food company
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's the umbrella group for Honwaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The softball circle Honwaka is a branch of the health food company Honwaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she is the company's poster-child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, she doesn't have much enthusiasm for PR work, and only appears once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I've never seen her play softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may have shown up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to see her regularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like you need to raise your position to a more suitable level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Honwaka, your rank in the circle rises the more you buy their products.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a high rank you can attend meetings only for high-ranked members,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that seemed like it'd raise my chances of meeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you want to run along the path of love, I can't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Who would go buying health food products like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that like saying she's some grand prize you can win if you collect enough box tops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, 30 portions of supplements and health drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Royal jelly is produced by the worker bees after ingesting pollen they've collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its rarity causes the production cost to skyrocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first heard the cost I thought it was a scam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I heard how it was made\N I realized it wasn't some fraud,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and comparing the price with other companies seemed about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only problem was that my own economic situation became somewhat unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the time I had to sleep disappeared, and I had to work day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's high quality stuff, just eating it all at once will,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the contrary, be bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take a lot, then any more than the set portion won't be absorbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the rest will just wash out of your system, or so I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about that, I was afraid of going to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for it was sure to leave behind precious nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you got sick because you didn't take these!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa's illness got better when I gave them to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the health food, my lifestyle got more and more unhealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's thought that healthy food leads to good health,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps I would have been just as healthy if I had done nothing but sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HA9A6A8&}"Popper Certificate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H3E9E45&}"Stepper Certificate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HCC6F41&}"Jumper Certificate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H2783DE&}"Winner Certificate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HA49A94&}"Wholer Certificate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H36D4F3&\fad(0,800)}"Plighter Certificate"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H0F1312&\3c&HE2F3F2&\fad(0,100)\be3}"Bee Missionary"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Healthy honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey candy for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be surprised, but two years had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hadn't seen her even once since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to obtain happiness quickly more than health, the environment, or world order...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How incredibly wasted were these past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no looking back on the incredible amount of money I earned and then spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirm with the barcode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the page is deleted, then it's an attack from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This honey candy will protect you from the flu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that was discovered by NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told not to tell anyone before it was announced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you mustn't believe everything you read on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to inform my dear viewers: this is definitely not my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you question my credibility,\N there's nothing to look into and I have no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the strain of these two years caused me to snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say tourists walking down Shinyougoku could hear that business was booming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to run from people's prying eyes,\N before I knew it I had come to Kiyamachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there an old fortune teller was emitting an eerie aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure she wouldn't give me any concrete advice, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrapped in unease, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I didn't ask for a consultation or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense you have much talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took off my helmet to the old woman's keen insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could tell it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I feel there's an opportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the opportunity that is dangling right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 5,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received any invitation to the national assembly I'd been waiting and waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The national assembly is said to be a two day, two night ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,deep in the mountains at Honwaka's headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please remove your blindfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The is the nucleus of Honwaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,built with the latest technology and techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is being targeted by spies even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take all care to keep what you see and hear to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We left our luggage in our rooms and headed to tour the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where we make the candy does not use any machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is 100% done by hand, with no additives of any sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To create something wonderful, it must be done by hand, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like 100% to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less than 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that a flag about 3 tatami in size emblazoned with "Danger!" was unfurled within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that we had a perfunctory friendly softball game
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then went around the organic farm and beehives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those that try to stop us for their own crooked profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that the righteous will be blessed in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all did great getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you all got some funny looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you had patches stuck on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's odd because it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unbelievers can't taste the amazing power of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all have found salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still much work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are approaching a time when the world cannot recover from the illness inflicted upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H0200E1&\4c&H088CE9&\bord1\shad2}"Global Warming"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H0494B4&\4c&HDEE037&\bord1\shad2}"Ozone Layer"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H0969EC&\4c&H039010&\bord1\shad2}"Declining Birthrate"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF000E9&\4c&HA90065&\bord1\shad2}"Sexless"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H4FFFB7&\4c&HD6462C&\bord1\shad2}"Earthquakes"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time of judgment is coming. 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFCF7F6&\4c&H0E4B78&\bord1\shad2}"Natural Disasters"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H1600DD&\4c&H020202&\bord1\shad2}"Abnormal Weather"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prepare for the upcoming calamity,\N we have prepared our "Ark of Salvation."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put a pair of each animal inside it and one pair of man and woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically Noah's Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people will board that flying ship and will live on through the catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after the destruction is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they will once again set foot on this earth and create a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad the world can't go on like it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I always worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, someone asks:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you worried about the final judgment that's coming?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, that's not it," I reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though the situation will be so hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what really causes me despair is the number of people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that do not change to a new way of thinking."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we only have a small, insignificant amount of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we must continue our efforts until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of those who struggle to the end without their wishes fulfilled
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will quickly return home to the Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After our bodies are destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our free souls will be reborn as new life-forms and ascend to a new, higher stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no need to worry about this troubling human life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, let me introduce my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H191B1A&\bord0\pos(956,372)}"Become a person"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it seems you haven't opened your hearts yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't continue to the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you spill out everything from the bottom of your heart and confront your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you all just lived superficially?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your life hasn't gone so well, that's probably the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my friends are successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they show their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truly great all understand this concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast out what you feel from the bottom of your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always going on about a diet while you're stuffing your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought your hairstyle was gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you don't need a girlfriend, but you're just unpopular, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had plastic surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 5,000,000 in my bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone out with more than 200 people other than my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wear a hairpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't love someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I throw up at family movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in crushing debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's untalented!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mess on the toilet seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in it for the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever loved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all work together toward our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're family of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ugly world, here there is true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my room later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you'll need some special guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H010504&\3c&HFCFCFC&\be3}"Emotion" "Victim" "Devotion" "Friendship" "Pure" "Faith" "Service" "Effort" "Health" "Love"\N "Hide Nothing" "Fraternity" "Bare" "Truth" "Reality"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite the spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently someone had hijacked the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we slipped into the dark forest to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the next stop along the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were even more people after us at the next station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seemed there were some\N non-Honwaka people mixed in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, one to warm you up, good customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't inquire about the details, but it seems this was the suggestion of one Master Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Neko Ramen then was especially delicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I slurped it up, tears fell from my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a worldly flavor I had missed so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided then and there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even if the world were being destroyed tomorrow, I would take myself to Neko Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go down the canal to the Kamo River.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in women's clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me with such a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm lonely and the river breeze is chilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lonely bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu, what in the world have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You head to the boarding house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have some minor business to take care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Akashi. I've brought a Castella from the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems things are over. It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Ozu's evil deeds until now have all been exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as a consequence he was thrown off the Kamo-oohashi and broke his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is one incorrigible fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. He's a slippery one to pin down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said that he'd cover for you, come what may.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your book, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this seems to be yours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it unknowingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a book I bought at a used book fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Ozu had borrowed it and\N never returned it, but I guess this Master read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been more than a year since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in trouble if there are fewer bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there'll be an increase in moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear-headed, in the engineering department, and smart enough to design airplanes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san seemed to have no fear, except when it came to moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me she was looking for her lost Mochiguman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is dangling right in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it! I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in this crazy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it'd be really scary if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did something like this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greater than the love Hikaru Genji felt for his infant daughter Kaguya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt fear the likes of which I'd never felt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, would I not have been happier staying with Honwaka?
